{"tid":1991905,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"又一家！美國石油探鑽公司Diamond申破產保護","createTime":"2020-04-27T20:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T23:43:06.000Z","uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c132556c16576b1ada5e23fb45ff1cbd7ddec2d0","tid":1991905,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200427/bkn-20200427103449005-0427_00842_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3c4ulT-lKIIXmk4WSpVB2T_3h_GeotIpKf3oZCYqUejVS1kHp8MuSaVXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200427%2Fbkn-20200427103449005-0427_00842_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3c4ulT-lKIIXmk4WSpVB2T_3h_GeotIpKf3oZCYqUejVS1kHp8MuSaVXM&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4RBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=62a22f88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200427/bkn-20200427103449005-0427_00842_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3c4ulT-lKIIXmk4WSpVB2T_3h_GeotIpKf3oZCYqUejVS1kHp8MuSaVXM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n油價近期大幅波動，令美國石油業界受到龐大壓力，繼頁岩油商Whiting Petroleum後，最新又有一家石油業者倒下！<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，美國探鑽公司Diamond Offshore Drilling Inc在德州申請破產保護，並表示已聘請了重組顧問。據悉，該公司負債超過26億美元(約202.8億港元)。<br />\n報道指，隨着國際石油輸出組織(OPEC)和俄羅斯之間的價格戰，以及新冠病毒大流行病引發的石油需求急劇下降，今年對該公司服務的需求急劇惡化。截至2019年底，Diamond Offshore Drilling Inc約有2,500名員工；在墨西哥灣擁有大量業務。<br />\n本月1日，美國頁岩油商Whiting Petroleum向得州法院申請第11章破產保護，涉及36億美元債務及73億美元資產。"},{"pid":"96994f3b870f35ac326dc8b267f22a8c04bd00b7","tid":1991905,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:23:49.000Z","msg":"無事 利好消息後 股市照升"},{"pid":"ea0153d9a09041a1eb175beaf077d3b2fce6b8fd","tid":1991905,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2978f4fa32cad622b3d7582b73c0f609b8dda76d","tid":1991905,"uid":196886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T20:25:23.000Z","msg":"少過預期，升！"},{"pid":"72288c3e6af98174a170f602e681764b46063a51","tid":1991905,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T23:43:06.000Z","msg":"Too small, who care"}]}